nestedClassifier.name: Distance on full charge and full gasoline tank

packagedElement.name: Category 1 of Ultra Low Emission Vehicle

sysml:Requirement.Text: The vehicle should be charging while braking.
I want to plug the vehicle into my house current and charge it.
I want to charge the vehicle in 30 minutes and drive at least 150 km.
Overall cargo space should be the best in the SUV class.
It should be comfortable seating for 5 passengers.
The vehicle should achieve at last 4,5 star Euro NCAP safety rating.
The vehicle should drive at least 1000 km on normal mode.

ReqIF_Profile:HierarchyElement.ReqIf_longName: Distance on full charge and full gasoline tank

sysml:Requirement.Text: The vehicle should drive at least 120 km on electric-only propulsion mode.
The vehicle should have electric-only propulsion mode.
The vehicle should produce less harmful impacts to the environment than vehicles running on gasoline or diesel.
The hybrid vehicle shall have the acceleration of a typical SUV.

sysml:Requirement.Text: When braking, the electric motor shall switch to generator mode. The wheels shall transfer kinetic energy via the drivetrain to the generator. Generator resistance produced from the electricity created shall slow the vehicle.
The vehicle shall emit less than 50 grams of carbon dioxide (CO) per kilometre driven.
The total vehicle mass shall not exceed 1500 Kg.
Cargo Capacity shall be more or equal to 1.25 m3
Car power unit shall have more than 200 BHP
